highlights.text: “SHE IS TOTALLY OUT OF MY LEAGUE (feat. Z9)” by P6ICK and Z9 is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #182.
“เจ้าของที่ (My Favorite)” by Mirrr has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 1238 days straight.
Only Monday has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “ทิ้งไป” is the highest at #27.
“น้ำลาย” by Silly Fools is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 59 spots at #108.
